scene.message:
Maki: We've got to hurry!{nl}
{ctl07:1}, you all won't be{nl}
able to get home!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Now that I think of it,{waitkey}the old man who invented the{nl}
machine was the only one who{nl}
tried to take responsibility.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Not that it matters,{nl}
but this place is downright{nl}
creepy!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: A woman's crying...{nl}
I've been hearing it this{nl}
whole time.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Are they all sitting{nl}
here regretting what they've{nl}
done?{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: The dimensional{nl}
passage on the third floor{nl}
was in a very unstable state.{waitkey}{clearbox}If we don't hurry, it may{nl}
become unusable!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Dr. Nicolai...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
he alone saw Kandori's true{nl}
nature.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's no use regretting now,{nl}
but we should've stopped{nl}
Kandori back then, even at{nl}
the risk of our lives.{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Are you after{nl}
Kandori?{waitkey}{clearbox}But it's too late. By now he{nl}
must be carrying out some{nl}
terrible scheme.{waitkey}{ret}
